{"tid":408881,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個matrix 係programming 用途","createTime":"2017-09-21T14:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T03:51:09.000Z","uid":13879,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5484eba831936ae3e8647ba6050d8fc50536f7f","tid":408881,"uid":13879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:54:13.000Z","msg":"如題！"},{"pid":"a981b5c44074f55ac3dceb816dbbe20b0903646b","tid":408881,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"R<br />\n<br />\nlapply 一行 做 transformation 搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1413b86144dfdefc8d32c497f17bf8ef9cf1f9e","tid":408881,"uid":148531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"硬膠子mode<br />\n<br />\n[code]<br />\ntypedef float matrix_t[2][2];<br />\n<br />\nfloat determinant(matrix_t &amp;in) {<br />\n  return in[0][0]*in[1][1] - in[0][1]*in[1][0]; // ad - bc<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\nvoid main(void)<br />\n{<br />\n  matrix_t mat = { {1, 3}, {3, 7} };<br />\n  printf(&quot;%f\\n&quot;, determinant(mat));<br />\n  return 0;<br />\n}<br />\n[/code]"},{"pid":"dbe4d8b243feeb50fb0d8315e3ce6d320e353707","tid":408881,"uid":105553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"Just a few:<br />\n<br />\n- Coordinate transformation in computer graphics<br />\n- Efficient evaluation of recurrence formulae<br />\n- Reed-Solomon coding"},{"pid":"bfb8d9029b4a1892d7f43294f3494e66c099e98b","tid":408881,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"fast fibonacci 好似係"},{"pid":"9e405e869dc6fc81c28d273dced9f387e3c6fb79","tid":408881,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬膠子mode<br />\n<br />\n[code]<br />\ntypedef float matrix_t[2][2];<br />\n<br />\nfloat determinant(matrix_t &amp;in) {<br />\n  return in[0][0]*in[1][1] - in[0][1]*in[1][0]; // ad - bc<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\nvoid main(void)<br />\n{<br />\n  matrix_t mat = { {1, 3}, {3, 7} };<br />\n  printf(&quot;%f\\n&quot;, determinant(mat));<br />\n  return 0;<br />\n}<br />\n[/code]</blockquote><br />\n係sem2學埋d lu factorization同eigenvector先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23f6eaed2503d76b1373ec9afae22615ac404a4","tid":408881,"uid":85524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"image"},{"pid":"635b50f3085503c95df0bd139adef47212b336e8","tid":408881,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"MATLAB with a builtin matrix-based programming language."},{"pid":"5951e11e3db2e5e7597c92553c44b1006ad50b85","tid":408881,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fast fibonacci 好似係</blockquote><br />\nAny linear recurrence can be optimized using matrix multiplication, not just Fibonacci."},{"pid":"9bb344b3d6837d1635741b7a3f404f789a6902b2","tid":408881,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T20:20:46.000Z","msg":"玩井字過三開。"},{"pid":"0c5a59f5f54b93c84aa621666a56be6c29ecd36c","tid":408881,"uid":52509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T20:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩井字過三<span style=\"color: red;\">關</span>。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bbe7652402d94ec2a64634353d6c17ea3c77e427","tid":408881,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T23:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>R<br />\n<br />\nlapply 一行 做 transformation 搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlapply用喺list, apply就用喺matrix<br />\n你想講apply(X,MARGIN,FUN) ?"},{